Window_SetHelpMessage
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Module:	<Window=>window/m>
#Line
#Wrap off
Syntax:	Window_SetHelpMessage
Veneer:	<window_set_help_message=>window_set_help_message>
#indent

On Entry:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = flags
r1 = window object ID
r2 = 7
r3 = pointer to message text
{f}
#indent

On exit:
#indent 6
{FCode}r1-r9 preserved
{f}
#indent
#Wrap
Purpose:	Method sets the help text for the window.  If r3=0 current text is removed.